    MPU6050.ClockSpeed
    I2C_MST_CLK is a 4 bit unsigned value which configures a divider on the MPU-60X0 internal 8MHz clock.

    Enum representation of High-Pass filter values.
    MPU6050.DLPFilterMode
    Enum representation of Low-Pass Filter values The DLPF_CFG parameter sets the digital low pass filter configuration.
